          <div class="foot"><span class="src">SUNY Press</span><span class="lnk">View →</span></div>
        </a>
        <a class="book" href="https://www.amazon.com/Out-Shadows-Socially-Bibliotheca-Indio-Buddhica/dp/8170308496/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          <div class="cover grad bk4"><span class="b-title">Out of the Shadows: Socially Engaged Buddhist Women</span><span class="b-auth">Karma Lekshe Tsomo</span></div>
          <div class="foot"><span class="src">Bibliotheca</span><span class="lnk">View →</span></div>
        </a>
        <a class="book" href="https://www.sunypress.edu/p-4016-buddhist-women-and-social-justi.aspx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
